'''PEGO YA BOBEGA DIKGANG'''
Pego ya gago e tshwanetse go nna le matseno ,mmele le bokhutlo.Fa o kwala pego ya gago o ka sala morgago tse di latelang:
* Tiro e o tshwanetse go e kwala ka kelotlhoko go ya ka dipotso tse o di boditseng

*Nna le ditlhogwana gore tiro ya gago e senoge sentle

*A go nne le tshedimoso ya se o tlileng go kwala ka sone 

*O bolele gore o dirile ditlhotlhomiso jang le se o se boneng

*Bokhutlo bo supe ditshwetso tse o di dirileng le gore o tla itsise batho ka tsone jang 

Ntlha e nngwe e o tshwanetseng go e ela tlhoko fa o kwala pego ya gago ke gore o e kwalela bomang.Se se go thusa gore o itse gore o tshwanetse go tsenya go lekae ka ditlhotlhomiso tsa gago.
